name: SATOSHILITE | Spells of Genesis | 2016
description:
SATOSHILITE is the first actual $LTC NFT in existence. It was made exclusively in collaboration with Litecoin.

Predating RAREPEPEs and Cryptopunks.

SATOSHILITE was issued on Feb 3, 2016 with an issuance of 500 cards. It commemorates the forking of Bitcoin to Litecoin by Charlie Lee - hence the name "The Imitator".
